<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.10">
<l>vārkoḷ meṉmulai maṭantaiyar taṭaṅkaṭal vaṇṇaṉait tāḷnayan</l>
<l>tārvat tālavar pulampiya pulampalai yaṟintumu ṉuraiceyta</l>
<l>kārkoḷ paimpoḻil maṅkaiyar kāvalaṉ kalikaṉṟi yolivallār</l>
<l>ērkoḷ vaikunta mānakar pukkimai yavaroṭuṅ kūṭuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the words of Kalikaṉṟi, guardian of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">its groves fresh with rain,</l>
<l>Which recreates previous speeches, knowing of the laments</l>
<l rend="indent">lamented by simple ladies, their soft breasts with bandeaus,</l>
<l>Longing with love for the feet of him the hue of the vast sea,</l>
<l>They will join with the unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l rend="indent">entering the great city of beautiful Vaikunta.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
